License: $149.00
Dependencies: None
Requirements: Vista SP2 / Win7 SP1
Synopsis: Adobe Photoshop Lightroom 4 software provides a comprehensive set of
digital photography tools, from powerfully simple one-click adjustments to
cutting-edge advanced controls. Create images that inspire, inform, and delight.

----------------------
PortableApps.comFormat
---------------------- &lt;a href=&quot;
http://portableapps.com/about/what_is_a_portable_app&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://portableapps.com/about/what_is_a_portable_app&lt;/a&gt;
What's so special about &quot;PAF&quot;? PAF runs naturally on your computer as if it's 
installed, and is able to use all available resources like RAM/GPU. But most
importantly leaves no trash behind!

---------------
USAGE NOTATIONS
---------------
* Select &quot;Use Default Catalog&quot; during 1st launch: afterwhich, you can edit
in settings.

Note: to keep things simple, &quot;default catalog&quot; is located @ My Pics when
running. When you close LightroomPortable, the catalog is copied back into
PAF and is located in: LightroomPortable &gt; Data &gt; Lightroom.

-------------------
SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
-------------------
CPU: Intel Pentium 4 / AMD Athlon 64
OS: Windows Vista SP2 / Win7 SP1
RAM: 2GB
HDD: 1GB of available hard-disk space
Video: 1024x768 display
* Internet connection required for Internet-based services

